Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.02,0:00:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.23,0:00:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.07,0:00:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.18,0:00:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.83,0:00:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:01:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.18,0:01:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.36,0:01:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom, stop the two of them. -Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.50,0:01:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stop it, Shibukaki. -Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.88,0:01:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Kenichi, Shibukaki. What is the cause of this trouble, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But Shibukaki keeps saying
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.81,0:01:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that the winner of this year's Japan Grand Prix Race will be Chebolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.77,0:01:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no one who can beat Chebolt from Yani Motors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Robio from Izio Motors is way faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh, what? Robio would lose at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-What? -Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:01:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! Who do you think will win?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon? What... Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Well. Robio's a great robot racing driver,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.63,0:02:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but Chebolt also has a great ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Make up your mind, Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... So you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The winning one will win and the losing one will lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what great weather today. Right, I have some laundry to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-Teacher's so mean. -Then, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think will win?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.94,0:02:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Which side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I... don't know anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't care who wins the car race.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. \N Robio will definitely win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-How come? -I'm with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, my Robio bank. \NMy Robio paper holder...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,my picture of Robio, \Nwith authentic autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're a big fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He talked to me. I'm going to watch his race tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, that's Robio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he? Isn't he awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But it must be dangerous to drive with a car like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder it if it has a \N collision prevention computer..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wacing cars are not ordinary cars. You knows nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Robio and Robiet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He broke the record of 10'04 per round. Good, Robio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,With this condition, he won't lose to Chebolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make him cry this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, Robio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's test drive is over. Come up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-Excuse me. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the room for Yani racing team staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the last room after turning left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-And... -Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ah, I'm... -Robiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Chebolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Robio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-What do you have with my sister? -Sister? Then you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Mr. Robio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you tried to do something to my sister since you don't think you can win the race, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I was just...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do that. I only came here to call you guys upon dad's request.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Step back, Robiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to see how great this "Hope of Izio" is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to have a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Robio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:05:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are the fool brothers of Yani!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You want to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce Robio to you, too. He's super handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Robio, it's me who you should fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, stop it. Don't do that, Chebolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Atom. Robots shouldn't fight each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care who you are. Step back if you don't want to get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Ox.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish the rest of this fight during the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ox, Mosquito, Robiet, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Robiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:06:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Robio, step on it like you are having a race.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Uran. We are not in a race now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, I'm sorry about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I got you into the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem. But why do robots from the Yanis
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Izios don't like each other so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Doctor Haruzo Izio, Japan's top car engineer,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,who made me born into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I had brothers called Lard and Drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, we were having a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Drill, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't do it, then they will do this to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Robio, since you were just born, you wouldn't know about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but these are the enemy of our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:06:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy of our family?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an unique characteristic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We become aggressive when we encounter certain type of robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-Why in the world! -Well, you'll see soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a characteristic we the Izios get born with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It is robots of Natta Yani, the rival of our father, Haruzo Izio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, we missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We should have stepped on those tin cans of Izio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to beat Robio in this race.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look forward to it, Chebolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-Count on me. -Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a call from the Science Minister, Doctor Ochanomizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Ochanomizu? Gosh. He's going to give me lectures again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yani! It's already been more than ten times that your robots have caused troubles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so? Then, how many times did Izio robots cause trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that is... I also warned Mr. Izio as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep causing problems, I also have a thought, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but did my robots kill people or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they destroy buildings or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only a fight between robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why! Do you understand? This is my last warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If your robots have a fight again, I'm going to disqualify
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you from Japan Grand Prix Race for negligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yani! Mr. Yani?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sick of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Izios and the Yanis have been enemies for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would even robots hate each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It is programmed into their electronic brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So they can never be on good terms?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's one hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is robot's register card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Every new born robots are to be registered at the Ministry of Science.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ah, this is Mr. Robio. -That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And another one. Let's compare this to Robiet's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,With Miss Robiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. Interestingly, even though they have different looks and sexes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-they have the same structure. -That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How can they be so similar when they were made by different people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Long-lasted rivalry is a scary thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-They now have a resembling technology. -So what would happen now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This cannot be proven scientifically,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but robots with the same structure
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,could be drawn to each other by the resonance effect of electronic brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So Mr. Robio and Miss Robiet, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There could be a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So if the two of them could get closer,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the Izios and the Yanis who used to hate each other could get closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Robio and Miss Robiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Robiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't. You are destined to be enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, it seems like Robio's going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be excited to have a big race ahead of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to forget about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"Natta Yani"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the house of Natta Yani. How did I end up here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go back. If someone sees me, I'll be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... The one who's playing the piano is... Robiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.22,0:11:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Robiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Robio, how did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I saw you for once,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,my electronic brain doesn't seem to be able to forget about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's strange. -Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I... couldn't forget about you either...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Robiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Robio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Robio! What is the Izio robot doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You surely didn't think that you could go back safely
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,after stepping into the Yanis' place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't do that. -You, step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:12:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! I have no intention to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared, Robio? Let me show you the supersonic power of my horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Robio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All you Izios can do is running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to lose you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to fight, but now I can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Be ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Robio, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Robio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Robio, Robio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Robiet. I didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Step back, Robiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-Step aside! Step back! -Stop it now. Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Robiet! Are you defending the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Robio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Robiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Robio. Robio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Miss Robiet. -Ah, Mr. Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-How's Robio? What about his wounds? -He's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Doctor Ochanomizu is looking after him, he should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this happened all because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he, Doctor Ochanomizu? Will Robio be able to recover?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the important electronic brain is fine, he will recover,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but it will take time for him to fully recover as a racing robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No... That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only three days left until Japan Grand Prix Race, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Robots aren't your tools!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I warned you that something like this would happen some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Reflect on your fault this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Th, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If Robio can't make it, then send me to the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:14:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you could learn racing skills in one day, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be thrilled if Atom could go in place of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to surprise the Yanis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, of course, I'll pay you full...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win the race, please let Robio and Robiet marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh, what? My Robio and that Yani's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the condition. If you can't accept it, then I won't participate in the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Th, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mr. Robio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are you all right now? -No, I'm not fully recovered yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but I got a special permission to go out to cheer for you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right? You are replacing Mr. Robio, so you can never lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Pressure isn't good... But I will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom. Now, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck! Yani will get crushed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Natta Yani!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruzo Izio!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, it's Atom. -Go Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Go Atom] Play, play, Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Go Atom] Gosh, I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Play, play, Atom! Play!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Shibukaki. Weren't you a fan of Chebolt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chebolt, let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You would be the right enemy of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand? We have to stop Atom from winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,While fans from all around Japan are watching,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot Grand Prix race finally gets started.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Each car gets into the most difficult course, the hairpin curve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Accident breaks out so quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Chebolt gets out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's at the head, going past other cars at an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! There's one more car. What a great speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Atom! Atom has caught up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As predicted, it's a competition between Chebolt and Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is the second stage, underwater hazard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it, interfering this race?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, you cannot go further.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mosquito from the Yanis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this electronic torpedo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's so bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mosquito.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Atom's behind. Chebolt's Red Star is running alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Atom? Is he out already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The course now takes place in a desert, with Chebolt at the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this tornado?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Chebolt, I made it specially for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.12,0:17:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Izio's Lard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-You can't go further! -Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Great distance between Mr. Chebolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's odd. There was no such tornado around this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be something again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-We are in the middle of the race! -Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your race ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mr. Chebolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chebolt, continue the race. Here, go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hurry! -All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! If you keep planning mean things, I will fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot... Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Teacher! -Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's back! Will Chebolt be at the head? Will Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Chebolt! And Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner is Chebolt with Red Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Good job, Chebolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Everyone, this race will not count. -What are you talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:20:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother and Izio's robots interrupted the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who saved me was
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chebolt, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, I wanted to fight rightfully with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chebolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.02,0:20:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Chebolt...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Brother! -Ah, Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Chebolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How funny. Now I'm the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? I'm the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Good. Then, let's settle this down ourselves! -As I wished.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.71,0:20:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make your Red Star into a scrap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Same for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous, Robiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Robiet, step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Robiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid! Robio, step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-Robio. -Robiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.59,0:21:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ro, Robio...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ro, Robiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Robio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Robiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-My Robio... -My daughter Robiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yani, Mr. Izio, you are the most foolish people in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your foolish fight turned both of them into like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-What must this sound be, Doctor? -Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a sound of artificial heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:22:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Robio and Robiet's artificial hearts did...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Robio and Robiet are together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.03,0:22:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-Forgive me, Robio. -I'm sorry, Robiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Their hearts will be together forever even if their bodies disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.73,0:22:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be undertaking a very important job.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I was selected as the captain of Mars investigators.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.66,0:22:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. I'm going to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.84,0:22:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You are Cavitt! You can't hide in like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Space men start showing up one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.87,0:22:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Save the Mars base!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "Adventure on Mars." Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.09,0:22:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy "Adventure on Mars"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.96,0:23:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.47,0:23:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.34,0:23:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.29,0:23:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.09,0:23:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.35,0:23:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.56,0:23:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.82,0:24:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
